# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if used with a power-user option like --dev or --system,
#   it might cause conflict.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock can be submitted to version control if you want.
